1.0.1.name: wordpress/zeecompany
1.0.1.description: zeeCompany is a slim and elegant designed theme with two columns. The theme supports Custom Logo, Several predefined Color Schemes, Unlimited Colors via Colorpicker, Content Slider, 125x125 Banner Widget, SocialMedia Buttons Widget, Dropdown Navigation, Theme Option Panel and more
